video_title: Speaker Pelosi: My Hope Is A Deal Before Election Day | Morning Joe | MSNBC
video_description:
House Speaker Nancy Pelosi and Treasury Secretary Steve Mnuchin are expected to continue their coronavirus relief talks on Thursday, and she joins Morning Joe to discuss. Speaker Pelosi says her hope is a deal before Election Day. Aired on 10/22/2020.
